SparseRecon includes code and assets adapted from or vendored with the following projects.

- SparseAGS: sparse-view pose estimation and reconstruction backend, demo structure, and reconstruction utilities.
- DUSt3R: pose initialization and related model code in the vendored dust3r/ directory.
- diff-gaussian-rasterization-camera: CUDA rasterization extension under submodules/.
- simple-knn: CUDA KNN extension under submodules/.
- liegroups: SE(3)/SO(3) math utilities under submodules/.

Keep upstream copyright notices, licenses, and citation requirements when redistributing this repository.
